replies.body:
Victims of the support role: {{champion:63}} {{champion:43}} {{champion:90}} {{champion:143}} 

The MYMU, originally called the "Immobile Mage" update (remember that?) , was supposed to address the issue of immobile mages being forced out of mid. That failed. Remember that straw poll that tons of people voted on and the overwhelming majority of people were in favor of balancing Zyra for mid over support? 

It's sad really. It's all well and good some mages {{champion:43}} {{champion:143}}  being able to go bot and do well, but not at the expense of their solo laning.
